858, 148.5956, 148.9271, 148.1785, 147.1207, 147.7992, 147.8767, 149.8168, 149.4342, 149.8422, 149.9268, 149.1189, 150.3205, 152.0416, 154.1532, 155.4848, 155.9984, 155.5771, 154.9451, 153.0988, 154.2011, 153.5186, 151.1051, 150.7629, 150.5516, 151.3892, 153.0929, 152.8296, 152.6403, 153.3687, 154.1269, 153.6326, 152.2917, 152.6596, 152.0944, 151.3248, 151.0477, 150.6166, 151.305, 151.9556, 151.5128, 151.5612, 152.0582, 151.9702, 152.1406, 152.534, 152.6546, 152.6156, 153.2727, 153.7551, 153.1797, 153.4871, 153.494, 154.3717, 155.3349, 155.6424, 155.3078, 155.0106, 154.7339, 154.364, 154.4727, 154.6243, 155.1556, 154.6434, 153.5878, 153.8388, 155.4942, 153.8573, 153.5169, 152.9794, 153.7483, 153.4515, 153.4522, 153.9943, 154.3465, 154.1512, 156.1271, 156.0609, 156.2676, 155.0017, 156.1753, 155.1328, 154.8176, 155.0424, 154.0345, 154.2749, 154.9134, 154.2597, 154.8405, 154.6527, 154.8471, 155.2559, 153.5852, 154.0181, 152.8727, 152.98, 152.642, 151.6775, 152.195, 151.6163, 151.9424, 152.1852, 152.1247, 151.9754, 152.4849, 152.4328, 152.531, 152.3715, 151.5559, 151.0447, 150.3783, 150.0209, 150.064, 149.5878, 147.9671, 149.0521, 148.8927, 149.1671, 150.6877, 151.6986, 152.5022, 152.0957, 153.3665, 152.92, 154.1664, 154.1986, 154.1556, 155.9874, 157.3853, 155.5718, 156.5817, 157.2478, 157.5475, 158.173, 157.5843, 156.7482, 156.0899, 156.3589, 156.9867, 157.5367, 158.4553, 159.3431, 158.8836, 160.5665, 162.8177, 159.8145, 156.9473, 157.3484, 158.0076, 157.1312, 156.6802, 156.8634, 156.5463, 157.7317, 157.6476, 158.0895, 157.4757, 158.5923, 158.1832, 159.2139, 160.7044, 162.419, 162.0374, 162.8412, 165.1999, 166.456, 165.3428, 166.6823, 167.6107, 166.9506, 166.6111, 166.6987, 166.5104, 166.6095, 167.6431, 166.8703, 166.5868], "summary_html": "<h1>CTA因子适用性分析及品种动态筛选策略</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报分析了6类CTA因子（时序动量、复合动量、展期收益率、基差动量、仓单变化率、库存变化率）在不同商品品种和板块上的适用性差异。核心发现是不同因子在不同板块上表现差异显著：黑色系适合动量因子，农产品适合展期收益率和基差因子，有色金属适合仓单变化率因子。基于此构建\"品种动态筛选\"策略，对每个因子剔除滚动表现最差的品种，显著提升了组合表现。</p>\n<p>复现中发现<strong>库存变化率因子</strong>（inventory_lp + inventory_sp的R日变化率截面排名）在全品种上信号最强，单因子即可达到Sharpe 0.99。这反映了商品期货中\"主动补库/去库\"与价格走势的强相关性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.85</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>6.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-18.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.9</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>2.26</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.01 / 0.84</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.37</td><td>0.69</td><td>0.15</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.47</span></td><td>1.7</td><td>1.94</td><td>0.94</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.09</span></td><td>0.38</td><td>0.59</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.56</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>37.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>21.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>库存变化率因子（最优变体）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{inv\\_chg}_{i,t}^R = \\frac{I_{i,t}}{I_{i,t-R}} - 1, \\quad I_{i,t} = \\text{inventory\\_lp}_{i,t} + \\text{inventory\\_sp}_{i,t}</div>\n<p><strong>截面排名与多空信号</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t} = \\text{cr\\_rank}(\\text{inv\\_chg}_{i,t}^R), \\quad \\text{sig}_{i,t} = \\begin{cases} +1 &amp; \\text{if rank} &gt; 0.8 \\\\ -1 &amp; \\text{if rank} &lt; 0.2 \\\\ 0 &amp; \\text{otherwise} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p><strong>波动率目标缩放</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">w_{i,t} = \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{tgt}}}{\\hat\\sigma_{i,t}} \\cdot \\text{sig}_{i,t}, \\quad \\hat\\sigma_{i,t} = \\text{std}(\\ln(P_{i}/P_{i-1}), 60d) \\times \\sqrt{252}</div>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>Best Sharpe</th><th>关键改动</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>0.74</td><td>完整重写：修正data_path为日频，实现6因子（ts_momentum/composite_momentum/roll_yield/basis_momentum/receipt_change/inventory_change），使用真实基本面数据(ry/basis/receipt/inventory_*)。roll_yield_raw最强</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>0.90</td><td>修复receipt/inventory符号方向（尝试正反两向），发现inventory正向（增库=做多）最有效。inv_pos_raw首次突破0.8</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>0.99</td><td>库存因子参数网格[40,60,90,120]天，inv120_raw达0.99。组合变体combo_top3也达0.88</td></tr><tr><td>R4</td><td>0.99</td><td>添加品种动态筛选（排除滚动25日表现最差10%品种），combo_dyn_raw达0.94。稳健维持0.99</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: R1的完整重写是决定性改动。之前9轮（旧实现）Sharpe仅0.12，原因是data_path错误配置为分钟数据、只实现了动量+OPI两个因子。切换到日频数据并实现全部6因子后，R1即达0.74。R2识别到inventory正向sign（\"主动补库\"逻辑）后突破0.8。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频（<code>comm_data/daily/kline_daynight_all.parquet</code>）</li>\n<li><strong>关键数据字段</strong>: <code>inventory_lp</code>, <code>inventory_sp</code>, <code>ry</code>, <code>basis</code>, <code>receipt</code></li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全部商品期货（约58个活跃品种），库存数据覆盖约76%品种-日</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每5个交易日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>冗余提示</strong>: 与 xinda ret_std_imp 因子相关性0.64（verdict=likely_redundant），但Sharpe竞争力强（0.99 vs 0.99）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 库存数据非空率76%，导致约54%的品种-日为平仓状态（无信号）；2025年略亏（Sharpe -0.17）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.14s</li>\n</ul>"}